{"tid":2206714,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"孕婦被防暴拉跌　警方：已主動交投訴警察課跟進","createTime":"2020-09-17T15:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T17:01:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"795c90ac14b321798071dcd4f08efefcf143b0b6","tid":2206714,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】孕婦被警員拉跌事件，警方指已主動交由投訴警察課跟進。<br />\n<br />\n太子站831事件一周年，警方在旺角驅散人群期間，有孕婦被防暴警員拉跌，需送院治理。民主黨議員涂謹申去信警務處處長鄧炳強，要求警方交代。警方回覆指，警員已按照武力使用原則，使用最低武力處理事件，理解社會對事件關注，已主動將事件交由投訴警察課跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405959&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNODe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=ddf812df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D405959&h=5f3f8517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=405959</a>"},{"pid":"808f2ee1d2ff39ea4f27287ace838e0635e31fed","tid":2206714,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d277b8fb091e960da11b46c1480127dce90b6426","tid":2206714,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfaa6cbc3a2a9aa29520aff4eb2941473c148e6a","tid":2206714,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d277b8fb091e96